=== Cultural assets ===

=== Cultural property designated by Ninomiya Town ===
* Important {{ill|lt=Tangible Cultural Property|Q2901860|qid=Q2901860|1=Tangible Cultural Property (Japan)}}
** Two wooden standing statues (sculptures) - Designated in March 2007.
** Tabune (archaeological material) - Estimated to be {{ill|lt=Nara period|Q189178|qid=Q189178|1=Nara period}}. Excavated in {{ill|lt=1915|Q2084|qid=Q2084|1=1915}} ({{ill|lt=Taisho|Q329174|qid=Q329174|1=Taishō era}}4) from a rice field in the former Shinto territory. Designated on June 5, 1974.
** Ancient documents (historical materials) - 11 items including letters and copies of letters of donation. Designated on June 5, 1974.

